{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But one thing I remember that my father was not allowed to buy-- not-- not-- that not allowed, but he couldn't get really nice timber for doors and other-- and furniture from a-- not a [INAUDIBLE], from the Polish saw mills, government saw mills, I'd rather the say.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father had to get a partner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then it was a suited partner with a Polish partner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were able to obtain that material from the government's saw mills.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were other saw mills, but they didn't have as good quality timber as those, yes, and that's when we knew there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we heard about-- please forgive me-- about Hitler and about anti-Semitism because a lot of that started of a lot of people were sent over back from Germany to Poland, the one who were born in Poland had to come back.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then anti-Semitism, but they are-- but where I was I didn't feel it at all because we were with the kids used to come.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We used to celebrate Christmas, and they helped us to celebrate Hanukkah and-- and then Pesach and all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, not in school, at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to come to our home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they couldn't understand why they are eating at our house things and we were not allowed anything from them to eat there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was the only-- only difference.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we had to explain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were only admiring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could have the lollies or an apple from the tree, but we were only admiring.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had, at school, a very big Christmas tree.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had in the middle of the town, a big Christmas tree and all that.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
